      "span_text": "This study did not include information about the causal agents of CAP as no blood cultures were performed to identify the pathogens as in other recent studies. [CITATION_1] Despite the fact that the identification of CAP causality was not the focus of the present study, urine samples were collected from all 124 patients.",
